<P>
A Bird In Hand: Five parrots named Sam, Barney, Miggsie, Loreto and Sharkey 
flocked to London's Mermaid Theatre Wednesday to audition for a Christmas 
production of "Treasure Island." Despite owners' claims that the parrots could 
talk, most of the birds perched on the leading actor's shoulder, could manage 
only a series of outraged squawks or deposit droppings on his pirate costume. 
