GOVERNOR; REAPPORTIONMENT -- UNITED STATES; REPUBLICAN PARTY; REAPPORTIONMENT 
-- CALIFORNIA; HOMOSEXUALS -- POLITICS; CIVIL RIGHTS; DANNEMEYER, WILLIAM E; 
CLUBS; BLACKS -- POLITICS 
</P>
