important." ; Photo, The poster that officially heralds the coming of Earth Day 
1990. ANNE DOWIE; Photo, Tom Bradley meets the crowd at City Hall at Earth Day 
I, 1970. BRUCE COX; Photo, Earth Day 1990 chairman Denis Hayes, an attorney, 
was one of the student activists who coordinated the original Earth Day in 
1970. TONY RUSSO 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
