<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY FOCUS: BUENA PARK; 
</P>
<P>
MEMBERS SOUGHT FOR FINANCE COMMITTEE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The City Council is seeking qualified citizens to serve on the city's Finance 
Committee. The committee consists of residents or business people in the city 
who have a background in economic and financial matters. 
</P>
<P>
The committee advises the council on short- and long-range financial planning 
and activity funding. 
</P>
<P>
These positions are voluntary, and no monetary compensation is offered. 
</P>
<P>
If interested, please submit an application letter to the Mayor/City Council, 
6650 Beach Blvd., Buena Park, Calif. 90620. 
</P>
</TEXT>
