</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
AUTOMOBILE THEFTS; ROBBERIES -- ORANGE COUNTY 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA102689-0190 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 126141 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
October 26, 1989, Thursday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
