performance of "Durante," the musical based on the life of Jimmy Durante, 
Sunday at 7 p.m. the Shubert Theatre in Century City. Tickets are $25. 
"Durante" was playing in San Francisco when the quake struck last week. The 
show's regular run opens Tuesday and plays through Nov. 19. ALEENE MacMINN 
</P>
